Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:04.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:05.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:23.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:24.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:26.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:29.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri! Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:31.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:34.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,W-well, in any case, let's get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:35.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:39.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:46.96,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(280,291)}Wake Up Call
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:56.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aa yume no naka de aetara yueru ka na?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:21.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, kanashimi dake sora kara maiochite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:29.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sonna koe ga kimi o ima demo kurushimete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:33.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Soba de te o kasanetemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:37.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kono omoi wa kienai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:45.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Futari me o awasetara hontou no koto yuenakutemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:49.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi no kotoba, dare yori mo sekai o terashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tonari de kimi wa "Sayonara wa ai shiteru" tte, sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sunao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:57.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi dake kodoku o utattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:01:59.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Egao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:01.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Arigato wa koi shiteru" tte sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:05.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ai no world's end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:25.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Chinami, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:27.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:34.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:36.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just bumped it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san, it's really not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Really, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We need to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:02:59.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:03.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:06.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's been an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't need a tow truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:13.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The bumper just seems to be dented.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:20.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You fell asleep at the wheel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad it wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:30.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Keep in mind that you'll have to pay to repair the guard rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Also, since you're a minor, we'll have to call your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's their number?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can we get in touch with them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:02.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:43.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan got her bandage off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:51.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's been coming to film club meetings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:55.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's just worried because she can't get in touch with Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've texted and called her numerous times, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:06.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My mom told me that Kouko's family canceled their trip to Barcelona.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-san, are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:18.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:29.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand when I run into someone and they give me a gloomy look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just pulled an all-nighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's going overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've been pretty damn disheartened lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your dark mood's coming through the wall, and it's pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:46.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened, but get over it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain in my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:50.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if all else fails, come see one of my concerts again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you in for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:09.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I said we should meet, and I'm the last one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:13.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan, your lip's healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:17.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a serious injury to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have work after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:29.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you guys had to accommodate my schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We had nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:36.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to check out where you work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:39.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You found an apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:42.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:46.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not exactly the dream home\NI was imagining, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:50.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The timing forced me to make a quick decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:54.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and after making several compromises,\NI'll be moving in this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:58.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I texted Kaga-san about it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:00.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:02.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, you can't get in touch with her, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:12.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My parents came to Tokyo the other day, and apparently, they met with Kaga-san's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:17.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think they talked about my injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:21.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san's dad came to my place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:27.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He talked about insurance, car repairs, and accident reports with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, he was really apologetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You hear people say it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Something like, "I got in a little accident the other day."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:42.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But are people really saying that about such a grave situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:46.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thoughts like that just keep swirling around in my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually pretty scared, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:54.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,One wrong move, and we might have all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:59.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san must have gotten in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:04.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she feels terrible about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's really my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Kaga-san was just as tired as me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and I made her drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:20.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It only became such a big deal because I got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's most at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was sitting in the passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:28.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I should've been careful and kept talking to her so she wouldn't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel responsible, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko wasn't used to driving yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:33.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I should have stopped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop looking so gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:45.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I asked everyone here because I wanted to think about what we should do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:50.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely don't want to break up with Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that to happen, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No one does!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:09:01.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, first and foremost,\NI want to know how Kouko's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:05.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but if we can't text or call her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:08.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, we should just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:13.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-san, you know where Kouko lives, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:18.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:21.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have work now, Oka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, shouldn't Banri go by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'd probably be easier for her to talk to you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:39.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where Kouko and Yana-san grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:56.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's very fond of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He follows me everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have work today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:02.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I had taken some time off for our vacation, but I gave that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:08.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Barcelona...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:10.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:13.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kouko never seemed interested in going, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:20.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:48.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:49.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:54.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for putting you in danger the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:57.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for scaring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:03.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:12.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's been really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:30.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We all feel responsible for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,None of you are to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:49.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've given serious thought to how stupid I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:54.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an adult now. I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:58.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can do whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And I ended up falling asleep behind the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,One wrong step, and we'd all be dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just your faul-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:09.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Falling asleep while driving is completely unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:17.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's the driver's responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:21.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I even let my parents handle the fallout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:24.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even realize how immature I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:28.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...truly stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too old to be a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I become an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You were a high school student until last spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:39.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can't suddenly expect to become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought I was an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I acted like I was an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:50.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I walked around at night, wore high heels and makeup,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:53.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,met with the one I love, and drove a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:58.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was just pretending to be an adult with the obvious stupidity of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:03.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I put everyone in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm humiliated with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't show my face to them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:14.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:15.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I need to take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:25.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even face you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:34.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:38.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean... you won't see me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:42.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The accident was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:50.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Saying you can't face me, you can't do it, you'll just disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:53.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not taking responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be forgiven?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:58.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,By me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,By everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Will that make you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you're saying you'll disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:07.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No... this isn't what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You got in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't do anything afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to feel ashamed about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:16.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But don't run from that shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:19.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You have to carry that humiliation with you and live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:23.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop being yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to pretend the part of you that you can't accept never existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you get in an accident again,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:35.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,are you going to say it has nothing to do with your current self and run away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:40.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Will you start over at your own convenience and leave everyone else behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,in any place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,to say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:01.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that from you, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:04.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:07.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You abandoned everything, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You left everything behind and started over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:19.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't accepted your past at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:28.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, who told me to forget about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:33.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who cried and threw a fit begging me to not face my past!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:43.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You said your former self was in love with Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:49.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What was I supposed to do when you said that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:55.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And stop talking down to me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:02.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It started before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:06.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You never had any intention of accepting your past self!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:09.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you abandoned your hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:15.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You left your family and friends behind and cut your beloved Linda-senpai out of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:18.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And you're living now like it's no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing it all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And next, you're going to cut me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you get in an accident and lose your memories again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:32.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be my turn to be abandoned, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It is, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A dream in which you abandoned me and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that because of a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:57.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being yelled at and hit... because of a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:01.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrible, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...sleep at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:29.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I'm about to, I have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A dream of driving a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm driving down a freeway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the passenger seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:40.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and partway down the road, there's a sign that says "get off."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:43.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I get off by myself, and when I turn around,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:48.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,the car drives away with you in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't chase after it, and just watch it drive away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:57.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, I feel like I've been having this dream for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'll leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:04.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that day will come eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:12.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you're worried\NI'll lose my memories again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:18.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave me behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:21.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know what I'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:27.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'll do, or how I'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:29.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:33.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you go somewhere, take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:34.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you have that dream again,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,do your best not to get out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:43.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do that, I'll do my best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I've left a lot of people behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:57.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've desperately tried to abandon the parts of myself I couldn't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:03.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've been saying "that's not me," and denying who I am, always running...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I wasn't even looking at anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Accident or amnesia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:20.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,you can't rewind your life and start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:25.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you struggle, you'll just hurt yourself, and the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:44.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri... sorry for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:47.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:54.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you because I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:55.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}K-Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:58.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you'll do your best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I-is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:15.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...my father standing behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:16.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:20.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's not there! The only one here is the cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's lunchtime,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:26.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,so I was just wondering if you wanted to join me for some ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:26.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko, he lied to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But he lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:48.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:55.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Just leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No honorific?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:57.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I hate everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Make this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:00.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:03.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How can you eat in this situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:04.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In these situations, we just have to act normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:13.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Both of you, get out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:14.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:16.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:28.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:44.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's having that dream again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:15.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Chigau yo mou, chigau tteba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:18.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aa, mada kizukanai no ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:24.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ni san jikan mo mae kara sono ude ni furetai noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:27.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I do not need forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:31.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:38.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sakebitai kimochi wa hora komaru hodo aru noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:44.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite doushite chittomo aa satotte kurenai no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:51.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ne hontou ni hontou ni watashi ni koi shiteru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:57.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kosabayui kotoba wa iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Han eikyuuteki ni ai shite yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:04.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gosen-nen go nado kyoumi wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:07.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi endless de wa nai no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:10.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuka wa shinu no yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:17.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Eien ni ai shiteru yo" nante yuwaretemo ureshikunai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:21.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mazu wa watashi o shinu made
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:25.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ai suru koto dake o kangaete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:40.97,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(55,412)}Return to Yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:30.30,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(93,361)}Wow, it's my first time being in Kouko's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:33.21,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(244,358)}It smells like Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:38.35,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(187,326)}The pillow being flung around
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:38.35,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(228,360)}smells like Kouko, too!
